    <h3><b>OZI SCRIPT</b></h3> 
Ozi script Is an easy-to-use web development framework that is built to handle both front and back-end web development. Ozi script is a components-based concept, meaning that everything in ozi script is a component and a component is a method or functions created to handle a specific task.
<br><br>
Ozi script is developed with PHP, PHP is a sever side programming language popularly known for developing web applications. <br><br>
Ozi script uses other CSS framework to achieve its front-end development which are Bootstrap 5, UIKIT and Animate.css. you can use any other CSS framework of your choice without using any of our CSS framework mentioned above, but we strongly recommend you to use the above-mentioned CSS frameworks to avoid any conflict between classes and ID’s.
Ozi script makes it a lot easier to code and manage your web applications without stress, with ozi script you cannot repeat yourself, with ozi script you can just learn about our code organizing and structuring and that's it, you can call any component from ozi script front end view.php script  or back end  create_bk_request.php script and that’s all that is required.<br><br>

<h3><b>WHY OZI SCRIPT</b></h3>
As programmers in this 21st century, its obvious that the web has now become something we can not ignore, and as we grow in this digital age programming is becoming more complex than it use to be most especially developing software’s for web, mobile and desktops, building software for web, mobile and desktop requires lot of efforts which include hiring more than 5 developers to handle a project , this is because every platform requires a specific programming language to function and as we all know the web alone has more than 10 programming languages that can be used to achieve a desired project, same for mobile devices and also for desktops, One of the most fastest way to build  software that can be used on web, mobile and desktops  is by using web development technologies, this is because every  mobile or desktop device can access your application from their web browser and with the help of this new techniques called PWA (progressive web application) its now possible to have features that can only be found on native apps on our web apps,  one of it is that  web apps can now be installed like native apps, receive push notification both online and offline and much more to come.  With ozi script is now easy to build and deploy your web application to mobile and desktop with just using the most easiest an the most popular web development technics you are already familiar with.<br><br>

